-home-exterior-270924-1045-01.jpeg 1280w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-exterior-270924-1045-01-940x711.jpeg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-exterior-270924-1045-01-800x605.jpeg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-exterior-270924-1045-01-768x581.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"640\" height=\"950\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-exterior-270924-1045-02.jpeg\" alt=\"A renovated home with a small front porch.\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA long screened-in porch runs along the back of the house and expands the living space when the large glass sliding doors are fully retracted.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1036\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924-1051-01.jpg\" alt=\"A long screened-in porch runs along the back of the house and expands the living space when the large glass sliding doors are fully retracted.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924-1051-01.jpg 1500w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924-1051-01-940x649.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924-1051-01-800x553.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924-1051-01-768x530.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1016\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/renovated-home-design-270924